name = "01 - First Mission"
text = "[i]Mission Brief:[/i]  
Welcome to the [b]Training Simulation Area[/b], designed to mimic real-life industrial climbing conditions without the risks. Today, your instructor will guide you through the fundamental skills every climber must master before entering real work zones.

[i]Objectives:[/i]  
[ul]Practice controlled descents using your climbing rope.
Learn how to identify minor system failures. Practice using your tool kit to fix simulated equipment.
Descend from the simulation cave safely. Complete all repairs and reach the bottom without triggering any safety alarms.
[/ul]

[i]Environment:[/i]  
- Simulation of a real work area in the depth.
- Multiple anchor points, ropes, and safety systems."
